juniErxSystemAgent.name: juniErxSystemAgent

revisions.description: Juniper-System-MIB: Added resource utilization notification enable/disable. Added KByte memory capacilty object.
Juniper-System-MIB: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names. Added resoure utilization support.
Added support for the Juniper generic system MIB.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniErxSystemAgent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 Email: mib@Juniper.net
juniErxSystemAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the System component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper ERX (E-series) family of products.

juniErxSystemAgentV1.name: juniErxSystemAgentV1
juniErxSystemAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component was supported in the JUNOSe 1.3
        system release.
juniErxSystemAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when new slot information objects were added.

juniErxSystemAgentV2.name: juniErxSystemAgentV2
juniErxSystemAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component was supported in the JUNOSe 2.x
        system releases.
juniErxSystemAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when the timing group was added.

juniErxSystemAgentV3.name: juniErxSystemAgentV3
juniErxSystemAgentV3.productrelease:
Version 3 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component was supported in the JUNOSe 3.0 and
        3.1 system releases.
juniErxSystemAgentV3.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when memory management objects and notifications were added.

juniErxSystemAgentV4.name: juniErxSystemAgentV4
juniErxSystemAgentV4.productrelease:
Version 4 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component was supported in the JUNOSe 3.2
        system release.
juniErxSystemAgentV4.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when thermal protection support was added.

juniErxSystemAgentV5.name: juniErxSystemAgentV5
juniErxSystemAgentV5.productrelease:
Version 5 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component is supported in the JUNOSe 3.3 thru
        4.0 system releases.
juniErxSystemAgentV5.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when the generic system MIB support was added.

juniErxSystemAgentV6.name: juniErxSystemAgentV6
juniErxSystemAgentV6.productrelease:
Version 6 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component was supported in the JUNOSe 4.1 and
        subsequent 4.x system releases.
juniErxSystemAgentV6.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when resource utilization support was added to Juniper-System-MIB.

juniErxSystemAgentV7.name: juniErxSystemAgentV7
juniErxSystemAgentV7.productrelease:
Version 7 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component was supported in the JUNOSe 5.0 and
        5.1 system releases.
juniErxSystemAgentV7.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when the resource utilization trap enabled and KByte memory capacilty objects were added to Juniper-System-MIB.

juniErxSystemAgentV8.name: juniErxSystemAgentV8
juniErxSystemAgentV8.productrelease:
Version 8 of the System component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This
        version of the ERX System component is supported in the JUNOSe 5.2 and
        subsequent system releases.
juniErxSystemAgentV8.description: The MIBs supported by the SNMP agent for the ERX (platform-specific) System application in JUNOSe.
